  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Deer Drive for the Nintendo DS is the first game to bring the thrill of arcade action hunting to a handheld platform. Deer Drive for the NDS is fast, fun, and easy to play but hard to master. With 125 power-ups and upgrades, 30 levels and a ton of animals there's plenty to see, do and shoot. But don't get too relaxed - Dangerous animals like mountain lion, boar and bear are just waiting to take you down.",
